item.title: Compiler problem here can some 1 please help me?
item.dc:creator: @Itachi_Uchiha Itachi Uchiha
item.description:
@Itachi_Uchiha wrote:

You never set your classpaths
My computer > Advanced tab > Environment Variables >new
Name put CLASSPATH and for the path put CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin;%CLASSPATH%;.
Now click Ok and click new again and set the variable name Path and the path put C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin
